{"tid":1682344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京重獎西九龍邊檢站一等功 原因不明","createTime":"2019-10-30T03:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T05:30:49.000Z","uid":26424,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e857e919edf6376a2dd4c574a28d9e3951329f41","tid":1682344,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:57:29.000Z","msg":"一等功基本上係公安武警解放軍嘅最高榮譽<br />\n<br />\n正常來講冇穿冇爛嘅人連續N年表現良好先有得攞三等功<br />\n<br />\n二等都要斷手斷腳半身殘廢 去到一等基本上要為國犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根据中國公安獎勵條令，在&ldquo;打擊危害國家安全和公共安全、顛覆國家政權、破壞社會秩序和經濟秩序&rdquo;，&ldquo;依法處置重大突发事件&rdquo;等方面，成績顯著，有重大貢獻和影響的，記一等功。<br />\n<br />\n央視稱，深圳海關近期打掉以海外代購、實為走私的團體，查貨名牌服飾、箱包、手錶等3,000多件, 先後走私奢侈品案值達3.2億元人民幣<br />\n<br />\n中國官媒環球網稱，至于西九龍邊檢站到底立了怎樣的一等功，已問過，但沒有問到，&ldquo;能寫的就這么多&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"00d80bd2d0b20d865e9efd4ffa941445e7e3d35e","tid":1682344,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv693.jpg&h=975a7fc9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ac61cbfffcf214f11019e5d0a1a6e80ff82b0f55","tid":1682344,"uid":11809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:01:05.000Z","msg":"運咗乜嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8bb52e6f6aa445be2b012c2ba9a92d355272a0","tid":1682344,"uid":198245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ac61cbfffcf214f11019e5d0a1a6e80ff82b0f55","tid":1682344,"uid":11809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:01:05.000Z","msg":"運咗乜嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"捉咗啲人上去"},{"pid":"20d4617ebcd8df0afd702e7828ee2952d166897b","tid":1682344,"uid":403,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4